Description:
create a new metric page

Usage: create_metric_page [-help]
                          [-after <string>] [-before <string>]
                          [-format {html excel text}] -name <string>

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-after <string>               # insert after the page with ths name
                              # (string, optional)
-before <string>              # insert before the page with ths name
                              # (string, optional)
-format {html excel text}     # config for specified report_metric format
                              # (enum, optional)
-name <string>                # name for page (string, required)